1. I installed nvm (Node Version Control) running the command:
```curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash```

2. Restarted the terminal by running the command:
```exit```

3. Installed Node.js 20.16 using:
```nvm install 20.16.0```

4. Finally, I installed SASS by running this command:
```npm install sass -v 3.7.4```